title: New York Color Smooch Proof Lip Stain, Berry Long Time, 0.1 Fluid Ounce
description: Lasts up to 16 hours. Precise felt-tip applicator allow you to line and define your lips with precision, then fill in with color. Natural flush of color, buildable coverage when layered to your desire. Water based formula. Wear alone or layer under your favorite gloss or lip stick.

title: Maybelline New York Colorsensational Lipstain, Bit of Brown, 0.1 Fluid Ounce
description: Sheer wash of color from water based pigments. Fresh, barely there feel from vitamin enriched berry nectar. Lipstain so bare, so light as air, it's sensational.
